        "TileImage": "$($repository 281790cc-8e45-4e70-9e28-056880f099bf).Image",
        "Description": "As evening settled over the reef, SquidwardBobi brewed a warm cup of sea tea and sat by his window. The water outside glowed softly in the fading light. He played one last gentle tune on his clarinet, letting the notes drift into the quiet ocean.\r\rFor a moment he simply listened—to the currents, the distant bubbles, the calm around him. SquidwardBobi smiled to himself. Life wasn’t loud or exciting, but it was peaceful, and that was exactly how he liked it.",
